snippet.title: L no Kisetsu A Piece of Memories PS1 Game Opening Movie HQ
snippet.description:
Opening movie of the PS1 game L no Kisetsu A Piece of Memories, a good adventure game that was only released in Japan.

Intro del juego de PS1 L no Kisetsu A Piece of Memories, un buen juego de aventuras que sólo salió en Japón.

Game copyright: Tonkin House (Tokyo Shoseki) (1999)

More information about the game here:
http://www.psxdatacenter.com
